title: I need to get some things off my chest
snippet: there are around 430 items that was worth tix on roblox and they decided to make a handful of them limited and i ask myself why? Isn't the whole definition ...
content: So i've found this wiki because i was looking through old tix items and i said to myself, in total there are around 430 items that was worth tix on roblox and they decided to make a handful of them limited and i ask myself why? Isn't the whole definition of limited items are items that was created by roblox and they no longer sell it? Why in the world would you make a tix dominus hat, a tix valkyrie and just completely forget about all the other tix items they've made?  That's truly unfair and very biased it doesn't matter if the item was worth 1 tix or 1million tix, their still considered limiteds. There are so much good tix items that you simple can't get anymore because it's literally untradable for no reason at all. I don't know how many items roblox has created and what are tradable or not but there's 400-430 items that was worth tix you can no longer get, let that sink in. Thank you for reading this and let me know what you think.

title: Why you can't reactivate your Roblox account
snippet: say you live in France and you have a day-banned Roblox account, and your ban punishment has ended. And you try reactivate but it's not. So ROBLOX HQ ...
content: Credit to this man: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WA_DuB_fGdwWhy you can't reactivate you're ROBLOX account.YouTubeSo this is why. Let's say your 1 day, 3 day or whatever has passed, and you try to reactivate but it does not say reactivate. It's because of countries and time zones. So let's say you live in France and you have a day-banned Roblox account, and your ban punishment has ended. And you try reactivate but it's not. So ROBLOX HQ is in United States of America, California, San Mateo.And the USA and France has different time zones. And Canada borders the USA and some states it's the same time but California and Canada has different also so if you live near the USA or in the USA your in luck.
